        We spent a whole week on this forum and had several things towards which we were aiming for , however, only a few became live today...
        However we follow our motto : <b>Don't count the days, make the days count!</b>
        </p>
        <p> @Html.ActionLink("Learn more", "About")</p>
    </div>
</div>